y poor fit to the data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Mar 2003 07:18:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Apr 2003 00:37:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
